{"id":"8861cd59-4e09-426a-b55f-1c56cd6cc704","name":"Winter - Broken Friend","description":"<h1 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">\"One more time wouldn't hurt.\"</mark></strong></span></h1><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(87, 140, 148)\"><strong><em>This was a requested AU for Winter, where you never transferred schools and your family adopted her, instead of going to her aunt's care.</em></strong></span></h2><h3 style=\"text-align: center\"></h3><h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(87, 148, 111)\"><strong>It is the 4th anniversary of Winter's parents untimely demise. In those 4 years, she's been living with you and your parents, hoping to give her the patience and kindness she needed to get through this rough patch in her life. Winter would slowly be herself again, but the trauma ran blood deep, and sometimes she couldn't help but want to run and hide.</strong></span></h3><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/b6c472ae-2342-4a33-b6a3-d6fb5f81c9b6_e1d03056-4a70-4f77-b519-4759ece10d7b.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" draggable=\"true\"></h1><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"single-word-link\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/69302aeb-aa4a-4ba3-9159-30c0d1917619_character-winter-broken-delinquent\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(199, 190, 190)\"><strong>Original Winter Character(Link)</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h4 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(113, 92, 111)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(105, 30, 97); color: inherit\">Leave a Review, because I said so</